Package me.taylorkelly.mywarp.limits

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Limit
    A creation limit for warps.
    LimitProvider
    Provides the actual limits that affect a user under certain conditions.
    LimitService
    Manages and evaluates warp creation limits.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DummyLimitService
    A LimitService that does absolutely nothing: Limit evaluation will always result in a positive response, Sorting warps per player and limit will return all warps created by a player mapped under a dummy limit. Limit evaluation will always result in a positive response.
    LimitService.EvaluationResult
    The result of a limit evaluation.
    SimpleLimitService
    A simple implementation to manage and evaluate warp creation limits.
  • Enum Summary

    Limit.Type
    The different types limits.
